zzapper wrote:
> Hi
> Having a Homer Simpson moment, but this must be easy to simplify
> if [[ "$LOGNAME" != davidr ]]
> then
> cd /o/inetpub/wwwdev/www.some.co.uk/epsystem/epadmin
> else
> cd /c/inetpub/wwwdev/www.some.co.uk/epsystem/epadmin
> fi
