> = .

cd \
${${${LOGNAME:#davidr}:+/o}:-/c}/inetpub/wwwdev/www.some.co.uk/epsystem/epadmin

although if LOGNAME is empty it's treated the same as if it were davidr;
if that's an issue it gets even more clumsy:

${${${${LOGNAME:-x}:#davidr}:+/o}:-/c}

